org.grouplens.lenskit.eval.traintest

Class CachingDAOProvider<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grouplens.lenskit.eval.traintest.CachingDAOProvider<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CachingDAOProvider.Item, CachingDAOProvider.ItemEvent, CachingDAOProvider.User, CachingDAOProvider.UserEvent

    public abstract class CachingDAOProvider<T>
extends Object
implements javax.inject.Provider<T>
    Caching provider to reduce the duplication of DAO instances in evaluations.

    This assumes that each unique DAO object is unchanging. That may or may not be a safe assumption outside the evaluator!

    Since:
    2.1
